# Windows: optional environment (User or system, or your shell profile).
# Enables tools and agents to resolve the Kinoite doc tree without hard-coding a drive letter.
# Copy: remove .example, set values, or paste one line into the Environment Variables dialog.

# Primary path (Windows path to this repo; use your own drive and folder)
KINOITE_WORKSPACE_ROOT=G:\workspaces\Kinoite

# Optional: NTFS directory for `wsl --import` when using scripts/import-kinoite-rootfs-to-wsl.ps1 -DoImport
# KINOITE_WSL_INSTALL_DIR=G:\WSL\Kinoite-WS2
